{"tid":97641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(衛斯理《大廈》) 躲浴缸被龍捲風捲到空中後安全降落","createTime":"2017-01-27T18:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T11:51:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00aad822299c21213fa7524ab6384eaf6c34de51","tid":97641,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T18:52:24.000Z","msg":"<strong>躲浴缸被龍捲風捲到空中 婦「乘」缸安全降落</strong><br />\n2017-01-26  17:16<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpABxUug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpABxUug.jpg&h=78913a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷取自《每日郵報》）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國南部日前遭龍捲風襲擊，一名75歲的婦人和兒子躲到浴室浴缸中避難，沒想到被連人帶浴缸被捲到半空中，最後老婦「乘著」浴缸，在家附近樹林安全落地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/jan/26/images/bigPic/400_400/phpQu3lbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fjan%2F26%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpQu3lbd.jpg&h=b782bf38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n威廉斯「騎著」浴缸，安全降落在家附近的樹林，身上僅有一些割傷和瘀傷，情緒相當激動。（圖擷取自《每日郵報》）<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，住在史密斯藍德（Smithland）的威廉斯（Charlesletta Williams）21日下午看到新聞播放龍捲風警報後，趕忙拉著兒子瑞奇（Rickey Williams）躲到浴室浴缸中。<br />\n<br />\n威廉斯說，她只記得龍捲風來自西南方，橫越了她的房子，把後半部都捲走了，也把母子兩人躲避的浴缸捲到半空中。瑞奇表示，只記得浴缸垂直上升、一直旋轉，無法說清處到底有多高。<br />\n<br />\n最後威廉斯「騎著」浴缸，安全降落在家附近的樹林，身上僅有一些割傷和瘀傷，情緒相當激動；瑞奇則掉落到浴缸6公尺外。威廉斯表示，「我告訴你，我不想再『乘』一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家氣象局指出，21日的龍捲風，寬度731公尺（800碼），風速達每小時209公里。氣象網站Accuweather曾在2011年指出，浴室結構較堅固，牆邊又有水管，有助對抗龍捲風，龍捲風過後，通常都只剩下浴缸留在原地。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1959466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1959466&d=ap59pJTNiO3%2Foi%2FwQdieB5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=97f07df1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1959466&h=21d89ce4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1959466</a>"},{"pid":"92b9216d3ded912141fcb80b138a2677bfae18f6","tid":97641,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T18:53:27.000Z","msg":"推 gh383844765: 為什麼聽到龍捲風來了會想到躲浴缸？ <br />\n<br />\n推 wolver: 那是美國房屋建材問題 沒地下室躲 最堅固真的就是浴室 <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1485425333.A.FA8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1485425333.A.FA8.html&d=ap59pJTNiO3%2Foi%2FwQdieB5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=006e9e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1485425333.A.FA8.html</a>"},{"pid":"6b47af3e4b4eddc901fa0d7e4a50aba9354a1b0f","tid":97641,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T19:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2219018ce3eab2504f805b11ad5af0bd961c33c9","tid":97641,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac56f23c12488eeea109481401ef1b50f5cbe67","tid":97641,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"原來大廈條橋真係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f7937c3674c935e6ce107433e4ae884dc8f9a0","tid":97641,"uid":19496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來大廈條橋真係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n倪匡講過全部都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教佢寫"},{"pid":"bd67774a8f98f2ae43f563f4793876ec198e771a","tid":97641,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},